     E'1. Click "Summary" tab\n2. Observe the table columns.',
     'Columns Date, Vendor, Type, Status, Amount are shown. Cost-code-only columns (Budget Code, Division) are not present.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

