     'A side preview pane slides in showing the selected direct cost details (vendor, amount, status, date). The table list is still visible on the left.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '2.2', 'Read', 'Detail page',
     'Opening a record''s detail page shows all fields and line items',
