     E'- At least one synced direct cost exists (acumatica_ref_nbr is not null).\n- Enable the "ERP Status" column via column visibility toggle.',
     E'1. Open column visibility toggle and enable "ERP Status"\n2. Find a row with a reference value in ERP Status column\n3. Observe the cell value.',
     'ERP Status cell shows the doc type + reference number as a link (e.g. "AP 000123"). Clicking the link opens the Acumatica URL in a new tab.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '2.4', 'Read', 'Unsynced ERP status',
