     E'- ERP Status column is visible.\n- At least one record with no Acumatica sync exists.',
     E'1. Enable "ERP Status" column\n2. Find a row with no Acumatica reference\n3. Observe the ERP Status cell.',
     '"Not synced" text appears in the ERP Status cell for that row (no link, no badge).',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- READ-ONLY ENFORCEMENT
    (v_suite_id, '3.1', 'Read', 'Create blocked — UI',
