     E'1. Click "Add Direct Cost" in the page header.',
     'Page title "Direct Costs Are Read-Only" is shown. The description explains records sync from Acumatica. A "Back to Direct Costs" button is present. No form fields are shown.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '3.2', 'Read', 'Create blocked — API',
