     'Response is HTTP 405 with error code READ_ONLY_RESOURCE and message "Direct costs are read-only in Alleato. Sync from Acumatica to add records."',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '3.3', 'Read', 'Bulk actions blocked — API',
     'POST /api/projects/67/direct-costs/bulk returns 405',
