     E'- Authenticated session active.',
     E'1. Send POST /api/projects/67/direct-costs/bulk with operation "delete" and an ids array\n2. Observe the HTTP response.',
     'Response is HTTP 405 with error code READ_ONLY_RESOURCE.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- SEARCH
    (v_suite_id, '4.1', 'Filters', 'Search',
     'Search matches vendor name, invoice number, and amount',
     'The search bar should filter across multiple fields simultaneously.',
