     'Step 2: Only rows whose vendor name matches are shown. Step 4: Only rows whose invoice number matches are shown. Row count updates immediately after each keystroke (debounced).',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '4.2', 'Filters', 'Search — amount',
     'Searching by a dollar amount filters the list',
     'Amount values must be searchable by formatted string (e.g. "1,234.56").',
