     E'1. Open filters, set "Date From" to **2025-01-01** and "Date To" to **2025-12-31**\n2. Apply\n3. Observe each visible row''s Date column.',
     'Only records dated between Jan 1 2025 and Dec 31 2025 (inclusive) are shown. Records outside this range are hidden.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '5.4', 'Filters', 'Amount range filter',
     'Min and Max Amount filters bound the visible records',
     'Records outside the amount range must be excluded.',
