     E'1. Open filters, set "Min Amount" to **500** and "Max Amount" to **5000**\n2. Apply\n3. Check each visible row''s Amount column.',
     'Only records with total_amount between $500 and $5,000 (inclusive) are shown. Rows outside that range are hidden.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '5.5', 'Filters', 'Combined filters',
     'Combining Status + Cost Type filters applies both constraints',
