     'Only records that are BOTH Approved AND of type Invoice are shown. Records that match only one condition are excluded.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '5.6', 'Filters', 'Clear filters',
     'Clearing all filters restores the full record list',
