     E'1. Click the "Date" column header\n2. Observe order\n3. Click "Date" again\n4. Observe order\n5. Click "Amount" header\n6. Observe order.',
     'First click: rows sorted by date ascending (oldest first). Second click: rows sorted descending (newest first). Amount click: rows sorted by total_amount ascending.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- COLUMN VISIBILITY
