     E'1. If needed, set per-page to **10**\n2. Click the "Next page" button\n3. Observe which rows are shown\n4. Click "Previous page".',
     'Page 2 shows a different set of records than page 1. Clicking previous returns to the first set. Current page indicator updates accordingly.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- VIEW TOGGLE
    (v_suite_id, '9.1', 'Navigation', 'List view toggle',
