     'Records switch to a card/list layout showing Vendor name, Invoice #, Cost Type, Amount, Status, and Date. No table headers are shown.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- FOOTER TOTALS
    (v_suite_id, '10.1', 'Read', 'Footer totals',
     'Footer row shows correct sum of filtered records',
     'The footer total must reflect the filtered set, not the entire project.',
     E'- Direct Costs summary tab is open with multiple records.',
     E'1. Note the footer "Totals" row Amount value\n2. Apply a Status filter (e.g. "Approved")\n3. Note the new footer total.',
     'After filtering, the footer total decreases to show only the sum of visible records. The total is numerically equal to the sum of the Amount column values shown.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- ERP SYNC
    (v_suite_id, '11.1', 'Navigation', 'ERP sync button',
     'Clicking the sync icon triggers an Acumatica sync and shows a toast',
