     E'1. Click the refresh icon (sync from ERP) in the toolbar\n2. Wait for the action to complete.',
     'A toast notification appears. On success: "ERP sync complete: X created, Y updated". On error: an error toast with a descriptive message. The sync icon shows a spinner while in progress.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

