     E'- Direct Costs page is open with multiple records.',
     E'1. Click the header checkbox (select all)\n2. Observe the selection count.',
     'All visible rows are selected. The selection count matches the filteredItems count shown in the toolbar.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- MOBILE
    (v_suite_id, '14.1', 'Navigation', 'Mobile — row tap opens detail',
     'On a mobile viewport, tapping a row navigates to the full detail page',
     'On mobile, row click should navigate (not open a panel) to avoid obscuring the list.',
     E'- Viewport is set to 375px wide (mobile).',
     E'1. Resize viewport to 375px\n2. Navigate to /67/direct-costs\n3. Tap any row.',
     'The browser navigates to the /67/direct-costs/[costId] detail page. The list is no longer visible.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- BACK NAVIGATION
    (v_suite_id, '15.1', 'Navigation', 'Back navigation from detail',
     'Back button on detail page returns to the Direct Costs list',
     'Confirms the onBack handler works and does not cause a dead end.',
     E'- User is on a direct cost detail page.',
     E'1. Click the back arrow / "Back" button in the page header.',
     'Browser navigates back to the Direct Costs list (/67/direct-costs). The list is fully rendered with previous scroll position or filter state retained.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- PERMISSIONS / AUTH
    (v_suite_id, '16.1', 'Permissions', 'Auth required',
     'Unauthenticated request to GET /api/projects/67/direct-costs returns 401',
     'API must reject unauthenticated access.',
     E'- No auth session active.',
     E'1. Send GET /api/projects/67/direct-costs without an auth cookie or token.',
     'Response is HTTP 401 with an authentication-required error message.',
     'HIGH', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    -- EDGE CASES
    (v_suite_id, '17.1', 'Edge', 'Invalid cost ID returns 404',
     'Navigating to a non-existent direct cost ID shows the not-found state',
     'Checks graceful handling of a bogus costId in the URL.',
     null,
     E'1. Navigate to /67/direct-costs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000\n2. Wait for the page to load.',
     'The detail page shows "Direct cost not found" text and a "Back to Direct Costs" button. No unhandled error or blank screen.',
     'MEDIUM', 'scenario', '/67/direct-costs'),

    (v_suite_id, '17.2', 'Edge', 'Record with no line items',
     'Detail page for a record with zero line items does not show the Line Items section',
